Subject: AIC Showing 'Unable to use to the SQL Server Database provided' error.
Description: Noticed the attached error appearing on the AIC logon page. Can still authenticate.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: Opening AIC to see the error message
What_We_Know__c: Shows up but doesn't affect anything?
Next_Steps__c: Wait for the customer to check the settings
Solution_Comment__c:
Cause
Outdated/Corrupted credentials

Resolution
I've adviced you to re-enter the credentials which has solved the issue.
